515
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:25,100
Better start shaking
that money tree somehow.

516
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:28,350
Well, the great peanut farmer
and rabbit hunter, Jimmy Carter...

517
00:29:28,450 --> 00:29:31,600
