522
00:29:39,800 --> 00:29:41,300
Your dad's a true statesman.

523
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:43,700
He can take out
that Hollywood actor, right, W?

524
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:46,100
Hey, Jimmy, what if I tell you...

525
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:49,600
