in the family business myself.

526
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:51,400
You're not talking about oil now?

527
00:29:51,500 --> 00:29:53,700
No, I ain't.
No, I'm ready to take a shot.

528
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:56,100
Because a sign has come unto me.

529
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,300
What has come unto you?

530
00:29:57,400 --> 00:30:01,400
