536
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:13,200
This, and right on my birthday.

537
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:16,400
And now that he's gone, boys,
the 19th District...

538
00:30:16,500 --> 00:30:19,200
...is in play for a Republican.

