540
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:24,700
Yours truly, Skeeter.

541
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:28,950
Hope you don't forget us little people
when you're in the Capital.

542
00:30:29,050 --> 00:30:32,500
Well, saddle up our horses, boys,
and send George W. to Washington.

543
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:34,500
Hey.
