00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,600
I gotta go give him a hand.

572
00:32:08,700 --> 00:32:11,400
George, got your clean laundry
ready for you on the way out.

573
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:15,410
Thanks, hon.
And thanks for saying it out loud.

574
00:32:18,100 --> 00:32:20,310
So, what do you do, Laura?

575
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:25,200
I read, I smoke, I admire.

576
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:28,800
When you do admire,
you admire what?

577
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:32,555
People who write, who read.
I'm a librarian.

578
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:37,200
Actually, I'm reading something right now.

579
00:32:37,300 --> 00:32:39,100
Yeah, a very engaging book.

580
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,500
