720
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:22,400
Okay, thanks.

721
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:25,450
Slight change of plans. It's out.

722
00:40:25,550 --> 00:40:29,290
We got a lot of work to do
before Sports Cap.

723
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:34,500
So, Karl, how long is this
History Channel thing gonna take?

